    <string name="terms_content">1. General Provisions\n1.1. These Rules govern the use of the FandoMatch mobile application (hereinafter referred to as the "Application").\n1.2. Registration in the Application means the user agrees to these Rules.\n1.3. The Application is designed to help users find acquaintances and communicate with each other based on common interests.\n2. Registration and Account\n2.1. The User must provide accurate information during registration.\n2.2. The minimum user age is 16 years.\n2.3. Sharing your account with third parties is prohibited.\n3. Rules of Conduct\n3.1. The User is prohibited from:\n- posting offensive, discriminatory or illegal content;\n- publishing materials that infringe copyright;\n- using the Application to distribute spam;\n- impersonating another person;\n- posting malicious links or software.\n3.2. The Administration reserves the right to restrict access to an account for violation of these Rules.\n4. Publications and Content\n4.1. The User is solely responsible for the content they post (posts, comments, images).\n4.2. By posting content, the User confirms that they have the rights to publish it.\n4.3. The content must not violate the law or the rights of third parties.\n5. Confidentiality\n5.1. Personal data is processed for the purpose of functioning of the Application.\n5.2. Data is not transferred to third parties without legal grounds.\n5.3. The User has the right to delete their account and related data through the Application settings.\n6. Liability\n6.1. The Application is provided "as is".\n6.2. The Administration is not responsible for the actions of users.\n7. Final Provisions\n7.1. The Administration reserves the right to make changes to these Rules.\n7.2. Continued use of the Application after changes have been made constitutes the user\'s consent to the updated version.</string>
